 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x71b0712291c0>([90])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x71b0712291c0> = [[1, 90], [1, 90, 1], [90], [90, 1], [1, 90], [1, 90, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x71b0712291c0>([1, 90])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x71b0712291c0> = [[1, 90], [1, 90, 1], [90], [90, 1], [1, 90], [1, 90, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x71b0712291c0>([90, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x71b0712291c0> = [[1, 90], [1, 90, 1], [90], [90, 1], [1, 90], [1, 90, 1], ...].count
